#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.static_assert"
msgstr "# triton.language.static_assert"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:4
msgid "`static_assert` 用于在编译时断言条件是否成立，如果条件不满足则编译失败。这是一个编译时检查工具，不需要设置调试环境变量。"
msgstr "`static_assert` is used to assert whether a condition holds at compile time. If the condition is not satisfied, compilation fails. This is a compile-time checking tool that does not require setting debug environment variables."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.static_assert(cond, msg='', _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `cond` | `bool` | 必需 | 编译时需要断言的条件表达式 |\n"
"| `msg` | `str` | `''` | 断言失败时显示的错误消息 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `cond` | `bool` | Required | The condition expression to assert at compile time |\n"
"| `msg` | `str` | `''` | Error message displayed when assertion fails |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:14
msgid "### 2.2 类型支持"
msgstr "### 2.2 Type Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:16
msgid "A3："
msgstr "A3:"

