#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:20
msgid "**注意：** `cond` 语句中值的类型必须为 `constexpr`。"
msgstr "**Note:** The type of the value in the `cond` statement must be `constexpr`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:22
msgid "### 2.3 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.3 Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_assert.md:24
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def basic_static_assert_example(x_ptr, BLOCK_SIZE: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    # 基本断言：检查BLOCK_SIZE是否为2的幂次\n"
"    tl.static_assert((BLOCK_SIZE & (BLOCK_SIZE - 1)) == 0)\n"
"\n"
"    # 带自定义错误消息的断言\n"
"    tl.static_assert(BLOCK_SIZE >= 64, \"BLOCK_SIZE must be at least 64 for performance\")\n"
"\n"
"    # 在static_assert的条件中出现非常量会编译错误\n"
"    # val = tl.load(x_ptr)\n"
"    # tl.static_assert(val <= 64)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

